Main:

A program to notify you of new album releases for each artist you have in a 
music directory.

Display options:
    Be able to display every cd, and its release. 
    Be able to set colors based on genre / artist. 
    Be able to mark things as hidden with a toggle hidden button
    Be able to star releases
    Show / hide certain genres. 
    Show/hide missing cds / aquired cds
    Calendar
    List (week / month / year)
    Most recent releases
 
Side:
    similar artists
        top 10 overall
        related by artist
        related by genre
    Pull in from last.fm
    Rename / move files
    lyrics
    cover art
    missing songs

Issues:

    Can MusicBrainz get upcoming releases?     
